ingredients.ingredient: 1 (12.5 fl oz) can canned chicken breast
½ cup shredded smoked Cheddar cheese

cookingTips: Press mixture firmly into muffin cups for sturdy taco shells
Bake at 375°F for 12-15 minutes until golden and crisp
Let cool slightly before removing from tin to maintain shape
